{"tid":2186928,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"PPTV拖欠1.6億鎊版權費半年，英超考慮終止合作","createTime":"2020-09-03T09:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T11:22:23.000Z","uid":30040,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6f2ada4b975974084b4cb7645a30537a0f23f3","tid":2186928,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"Another key fact in this issue: Premier League will consider terminating Chinese TV contract with PPTV one year into 3-yr deal as &pound;160million now nearly six months overdue:<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/martynziegler/status/1301199346025848839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fmartynziegler%2Fstatus%2F1301199346025848839&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hdArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=a9ada812\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fmartynziegler%2Fstatus%2F1301199346025848839&h=6bb17775\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/martynziegler/status/1301199346025848839</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2013年10月，<span class=\"red\">蘇寧</span>雲商與聯想集團旗下弘毅資本聯手，斥資4.2億美元（約33億港元）入股PPTV，蘇寧將成為PPTV單一最大股東。根據交易條款，蘇寧雲商及弘毅資本將分別出資2.5億及1.7億美元，交易完成後，蘇寧將持有PPTV約44%股權，成為大股東，弘毅則占29.9%，相當於PPTV整體估值約5.68億美元（約44.3億港元）。[6]之後由於樂視深陷財務危機，PPTV接手了原樂視體育的部分資源。<br />\n<br />\n2018年，更名為PP影片。這一年，PP影片首次獲得了歐洲五大聯賽[7][8][9]以及歐冠聯賽、歐聯杯全部比賽的轉播權，但這一局面僅維持了一年。2019-20賽季開始，蘇寧體育獲得了未來三年的英超獨家版權的同時，也失去了西甲聯賽的相應權利，導致PP體育不再影片直播西甲賽事。[10]"},{"pid":"39dbe30982ec2a0c15076d211829818145e13eec","tid":2186928,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"蘇寧早兩年唔係好撚威架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8203df814ba22a11387fa5d16be62d4e49a3bbcf","tid":2186928,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:24:57.000Z","msg":"蘇寧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgm